title: Dj xAvIeRRe in sessions 2008(3cd)MaKina forever
description: Estas son 3 sesiones dedicadas a los fiesteros de barcelona y alrededores, que aun quedamos algunos que como yo disfrutemos y seguimos disfrutando de la musica makina.La epoca dorada de discotecas como Spook, Barraca,Pont aeri,Xque,Actv,Bypass y muchas mas, que hicieron unirnos como una gran familia.Un saludo Fisteros y espero que os guste.Dj XaVieRRe Makina forever.                                                                                                                            These are 3 sessions dedicated to the fiesteros of Barcelona and the environs, that we were even some that as I enjoy and continued enjoying music makina. The age sea bream of discotheques like Spook, Cabin, Pont aeri, Xque, Actv, Bypass and many but, that made unite to us like a great family. A Fisteros greeting and I hope that you like. Dj XaVieRRe Makina to forever.
